import React from 'react';
import { Accordion, AccordionItem, AccordionButton, AccordionPanel } from 'react-accordion';

function Question() {
  return (
    <Accordion>
      <AccordionItem>
        <AccordionButton>Öğe 1</AccordionButton>
        <AccordionPanel>
          İçerik 1
        </AccordionPanel>
      </AccordionItem>
      <AccordionItem>
        <AccordionButton>Öğe 2</AccordionButton>
        <AccordionPanel>
          İçerik 2
        </AccordionPanel>
      </AccordionItem>
      <AccordionItem>
        <AccordionButton>Öğe 3</AccordionButton>
        <AccordionPanel>
          İçerik 3
        </AccordionPanel>
      </AccordionItem>
    </Accordion>
  );
}

export default App;
